title: That Francis W. Patience of Latham, New York, be, and he hereby is elected Secretary of the Senate for the years 2011-2012
fulltext:
SENATE  RESOLUTION that Francis W. Patience of Latham, New York, be, and
he hereby is elected Secretary of the Senate for the years 2011-2012

RESOLVED, That Francis W. Patience of Latham, New York, be, and he here-
by is elected Secretary of the Senate for the years 2011-2012.
